name: Strength in Love - EP
description:
Buy Gaz Simmonds' debut EP. Now 
only £4, (RRP £5.99). Featuring 6 tracks Produced by Andy Baker of Resound Media. Featuring songs co-written with Philippa Hanna, Andy Baker and Rich White. 

50p OF EVERY CD BOUGHT ONLINE GOES STRAIGHT TO TURN ON THE TAP.

http://www.turnonthetap.org.uk/

Turn on the Tap is a project run by Samaritans Purse, who strive to provide safe, clean water for families in africa. Roughly £50 will provide one family water for life. So your donation will go a long way when you think that £10 or less will provide one person clean water for life.

Track Listing:

1. He's Alive
2. Stronger
3. Faithful
4. Joy can be found
5. You took the fall
6. Let it be loud
